dct_title_s: Mobil cruising guide : Montreal, Canada to Key West, Florida including Hudson River, New Jersey Coast, Delaware and Chesapeake Bay.
dct_description_sm: Includes pictorial vignettes of some sites and lighthouses and aids to navigation. Federal waterway markers, intracoastal beacons, uniform state waterway marking systems, mileage distances, points of interest etc. etc. in margins.
